data.meta_description:
68 likes, 1 comments - eccobooks on October 11, 2023: "Jonathan Lethem, the bestselling author of big literary hits such as THE FORTRESS OF SOLITUDE and MOTHERLESS BROOKLYN, is back with a new book!

In a love letter of a review for the @latimes, Lauren LeBlanc writes: â€œBROOKLYN CRIME NOVEL surveys the deep fissures that surface when the pull of home is stronger than nostalgia. . . . the novel is also an endless declaration of love. Every neighborhood deserves such a discursive portrait, such ruthless devotion and such an audacious book." Read the full review by going to the link in our bio or bit.ly/LATIMESJL.".
